<n:tr>
<n:td>
We have a screen which was working fine in ZK2.4.1. One of its sections
is a Grid inside a Groupbox.

With ZK3.0, this section continues to work fine in FF, and in fact looks
more appealing.

However in IE it is a nightmare: the Grid floats half out of the Groupbox,
obscuring the caption completely and leaving an ugly empty blue section
underneath.
</n:td>
</n:tr>
	</n:table>
